include ../card.pug
section#business-plan
  div(class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl flex flex-col gap-10 px-[10px] py-5 lg:px-10 lg:py-10 xl:px-4 xl:py-[60px]")
    div(class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center")
      h2(class="mb-5 text-2xl font-semibold") 
        | Bring your business plan to life
      p(class="text-neutral-500")
        | Abacum is everything finance teams need to forecast revenue, plan headcount, or budget OPEX. Easily define metrics, change assumptions, and adjust headcount from an intuitive interface.
    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-3")
      +card("business-plan", "../src/static/images/image.webp", "Finally, formulas you can understand", "Model your metrics with formulas you can easily understand and trace. Abacum delivers precision and accuracy at scale.")
      +card("business-plan", "../src/static/images/image-1.webp", "Always have a what-if answer", "Compare different plans and outcomes and decide the best strategies to hit your ambitious goals.")
      +card("business-plan", "../src/static/images/image-2-1.webp", "Have full control over any change", "With permissions and traceability never lose control over who made an edit.")